The paper focuses on using computer vision to detect subtle facial expressions, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The use of machine learning algorithms and feature extraction methods also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with micro-movements, which could be considered a sub-topic of multimedia (cs.MM).
